trans-unit.source: Represents the results of compilation that are returned from a compiler.
trans-unit.target: Representerer resultatene av kompilering som er returnert fra en kompilator.

trans-unit.source: This class contains the following information about the results of a compilation by an <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler> interface implementation: - The <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.CompiledAssembly%2A> property indicates the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen inneholder følgende informasjon om resultatet av en samling av en <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler>grensesnitt implementering: - <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.CompiledAssembly%2A>egenskapen angir kompilerte samlingen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.CompiledAssembly%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.ICodeCompiler>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.Evidence%2A> property indicates the security evidence for the assembly.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.Evidence%2A>Egenskapen angir sikkerhetsbevis for samlingen.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.Evidence%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.PathToAssembly%2A> property indicates the path to the compiled assembly, if it was not generated only in memory.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.PathToAssembly%2A>Egenskapen angir banen til den kompilerte samlingen hvis den ikke ble generert bare i minnet.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.PathToAssembly%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.Errors%2A> property indicates any compiler errors and warnings.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.Errors%2A>Egenskapen angir eventuelle kompilatorfeil og advarsler.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.Errors%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.Output%2A> property contains the compiler output messages.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.Output%2A>Egenskapen inneholder kompilatoren utdata meldinger.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.Output%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.NativeCompilerReturnValue%2A> property indicates result code value returned by the compiler.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.NativeCompilerReturnValue%2A>Egenskapen angir resultatet code-verdien som returneres av kompilatoren.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.NativeCompilerReturnValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.TempFiles%2A> property indicates the temporary files generated during compilation and linking.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.TempFiles%2A>Egenskapen angir midlertidige filer som er generert under kompilering og koble.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults.TempFiles%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This class contains an inheritance demand at the class level that applies to all members.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne klassen inneholder en arv behov på klassen nivået som gjelder for alle medlemmer.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Security.SecurityException> is thrown when the derived class does not have full-trust permission.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Security.SecurityException>forårsakes når den utledede klassen ikke har tillatelse for fullstendig klarering.</xref:System.Security.SecurityException>

trans-unit.source: For details about inheritance demands, see [Inheritance Demands](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28b9adbb-8f08-4f10-b856-dbf59eb932d9).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om arv krav, kan du se [arv krav](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28b9adbb-8f08-4f10-b856-dbf59eb932d9).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults"></xref> class that uses the specified temporary files.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerResults"> </xref> klasse som bruker de angitte midlertidige filene.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection"></xref> with which to manage and store references to intermediate files generated during compilation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection"> </xref> som til å administrere og lagre referanser til midlertidige filer som er generert under kompilering.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir kompilerte samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Reflection.Assembly> that indicates the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Reflection.Assembly>som angir kompilerte samlingen.</xref:System.Reflection.Assembly>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of compiler errors and warnings.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av kompilatorfeil og advarsler.

trans-unit.source: File and line number information is associated with each <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerError>, so that user code to locate and display the code that generated an error or warning, where possible, can be implemented.
trans-unit.target: Fil- og linje nummer informasjonen er knyttet til hver <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerError>, slik at brukerkode finner og viser koden som genereres en feil eller advarsel, der det er mulig kan implementeres.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerError>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerErrorCollection"></xref> that indicates the errors and warnings resulting from compilation, if any.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerErrorCollection"> </xref> som angir feillogg fra kompileringen, hvis noen.

trans-unit.source: Indicates the evidence object that represents the security policy permissions of the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: Angir bevis-objektet som representerer policy sikkerhetstillatelser for kompilerte samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Security.Policy.Evidence"></xref> object that represents the security policy permissions of the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Policy.Evidence"> </xref> objektet som representerer policy sikkerhetstillatelser for kompilerte samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the compiler's return value.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir verdien som returneres av kompilatoren.

trans-unit.source: This property contains the numeric exit code returned by a command line compiler, if implemented.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen inneholder numeriske avsluttingskoden returnert av en kommandolinje kompilator Hvis implementert.

trans-unit.source: A value of 0 indicates success, while a non-zero value indicates failure.
trans-unit.target: Verdien 0 indikerer var vellykket, mens en ikke-null-verdi som angir feilen.

trans-unit.source: The compiler's return value.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som returneres av kompilatoren.

trans-unit.source: Gets the compiler output messages.
trans-unit.target: Henter kompilatoren utdata meldinger.

trans-unit.source: If the compiler returned no messages, the value of this property will be an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis kompilatoren returnerte ingen meldinger, være verdien for denne egenskapen en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection"></xref> that contains the output messages.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection"> </xref> som inneholder output-meldinger.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the path of the compiled assembly.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir banen til den kompilerte samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The path of the assembly, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if the assembly was generated in memory.
trans-unit.target: Banen til samlingen, eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> hvis samlingen ble generert i minnet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the temporary file collection to use.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir samlingen midlertidig fil for å bruke.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection"></xref> with which to manage and store references to intermediate files generated during compilation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.TempFileCollection"> </xref> som til å administrere og lagre referanser til midlertidige filer som er generert under kompilering.
